'''二十碳五烯酸'''（{{lang-en|Eicosapentaenoic acid, EPA}}）是有五個[[雙鍵|雙鍵]]的[[多元不飽和脂肪|多元不飽和脂肪酸]]（C<sub>20</sub>H<sub>30</sub>O<sub>2</sub>），是一种[[ω-3脂肪酸|ω-3脂肪酸]]。

==来源==
在人类饮食中，这种脂肪酸主要来源于食用脂肪含量高的[[鱼类|鱼类]]和[[鱼油|鱼油]]，例如[[鳕鱼|鳕鱼肝]]、[[青鱼|青鱼]]、[[鲭鱼|鲭鱼]]、[[鲑鱼|鲑鱼]]、[[鲱鱼|鲱鱼]]、[[沙丁鱼|沙丁鱼]]和多种可食用[[海草|海草]]和[[浮游植物|浮游植物]]；在人类[[母乳|母乳]]中亦存在此种脂肪酸。

但是鱼类自身并不合成EPA，而是通过食用[[海藻|海藻]]摄取<ref>Yvonne Bishop-Weston. "Plant based sources of vegan & vegetarian Docosahexaenoic acid - DHA and Eicosapentaenoic acid EPA & Essential Fats". Retrieved 2008-08-05.</ref>。人类也可通过非动物性来源获取EPA，例如微藻类。此类植物亦被培养成为一个商业化的EPA来源<ref>Jess Halliday (12/01/2007). "Water 4 to introduce algae DHA/EPA as food ingredient". Retrieved 2007-02-09.</ref>。EPA在高大植物中不常见，但是有报道称[[马齿苋|马齿苋]]含微量EPA<ref>Simopoulos, Artemis P (2002). "Omega-3 fatty acids in wild plants, nuts and seeds". Asia Pacific Journal of Clinical Nutrition 11 (Suppl 2): S163–73.</ref>。2013年曾有报道指出[[亚麻荠属|亚麻荠属]]植物的一种[[基因改造|基因改造]]变种含有大量EPA<ref>Ruiz-Lopez, N.; Haslam, R. P.; Napier, J. A.; Sayanova, O. (January 2014). "Successful high-level accumulation of fish oil omega-3 long-chain polyunsaturated fatty acids in a transgenic oilseed crop". The Plant Journal 77 (2): 198–208.</ref><ref>Coghlan, Andy (4 January 2014) "Designed plant oozes vital fish oils"' New Scientist, volume 221, issue 2950, page 12.</ref>。

人体能够利用[[α-亚麻酸|α-亚麻酸]]（[[ALA|ALA]]）合成自身所需的EPA。ALA是人体的一种必需脂肪酸，必须确保充足的摄入。但是，将ALA转化至EPA的效率远低于从食物中直接摄取，因为EPA本身也用于进一步合成[[二十二碳六烯酸|二十二碳六烯酸]]（[[DHA|DHA]]）。人体很难从不含EPA和DHA的食物中间接获取足够量的EPA，因为：1.身体需要额外的代谢过程来合成EPA; 2.EPA同时又被用于合成DHA。某些疾病或者特殊条件会显著地降低身体从ALA合成EPA的能力，例如糖尿病或者一些过敏反应。

==临床意义==
[[美国国家卫生研究院|美国国家卫生研究院]]的[[MedlinePlus|MedlinePlus]]数据库列出了EPA（单独使用或联合其他omega-3脂肪酸使用）能够有效治疗的疾病<ref>NIH Medline Plus. "MedlinePlus Herbs and Supplements: Omega-3 fatty acids, fish oil, alpha-linolenic acid". Retrieved February 14, 2006.</ref>。大多数情况下EPA被证明对发炎症状有效。

在所有omega-3脂肪酸中，EPA被认为对一些精神方面的疾病有潜在的疗效，例如[[精神分裂症|精神分裂症]]<ref>Peet M, Brind J, Ramchand CN, Shah S, Vankar GK (2001). "Two double-blind placebo-controlled pilot studies of eicosapentaenoic acid in the treatment of schizophrenia". Schizophrenia Research 49 (3): 243–51.</ref><ref>Song C, Zhao S (Oct 2007). "Omega-3 fatty acid eicosapentaenoic acid. A new treatment for psychiatric and neurodegenerative diseases: a review of clinical investigations". Expert Opin Investig Drugs 16 (10): 1627–38.</ref>。

有研究表明EPA有可能对改进[[抑郁|抑郁]]状态有帮助。2009年的一个综合研究发现摄取更高EPA:DHA比例的omega-3补充剂的病人较少出现抑郁症状<ref>Martins, JG (Oct 2009). "EPA but not DHA appears to be responsible for the efficacy of omega-3 long chain polyunsaturated fatty acid supplementation in depression: evidence from a meta-analysis of randomized controlled trials.". Journal of the American College of Nutrition 28 (5): 525–42.</ref>。

==对人体健康的影响==
=== 总体效果===
摄入脂肪酸对慢性病的影响被广泛认可，这些疾病包括[[肥胖症|肥胖症]]、[[糖尿病|糖尿病]]、[[癌症|癌症]]、[[关节炎|关节炎]]、[[哮喘|哮喘]]和[[心血管疾病|心血管疾病]]<ref>Recent trends in the advanced analysis of bioactive fatty acids.Ruiz-Rodriguez A, Reglero G, Ibañez E.Departamento de Caracterización de Alimentos, Instituto de Fermentaciones Industriales, CSIC, Juan de la Cierva, 3, E-28006 Madrid, Spain.</ref>。

===对神经系统的影响===
足够的脂肪酸摄入（特别是EPA和DHA）对胎儿神经系统发育成熟的重要性如今已被证明<ref>Ghisolfi J., 1997. Acides gras, croissance fœtale et grossesse. Arch Pediatr 1997;4 (suppl 2):133s-5s.</ref>。

===炎症===
一个研究表明鱼油（通常含有较高的EPA和DHA含量）可以通过影响多种发炎反应的机理而预防这类疾病<ref>Fish oil lipid emulsions and immune response: what clinicians need to know.Waitzberg DL, Torrinhas RS.Faculdade de Medicina da Universidade de São Paulo, Avenida Dr Arnaldo, 455-2 degrees andar, sala 2108, CEP: 01245-903, São Paulo, SP, Brasil; PMID 19605803 [archive] [PubMed - in process]</ref>。

=== 心血管疾病===
对于心血管方面的疾病，EPA和DHA被证明对改进以下症状有效<ref>Cardiovascular disease prevention and treatment.von Schacky C.Preventive Cardiology, Medizinische Clinic and Policlinic Innenstadt, University of Munich, Ziemssensstr. 1, D-80336 Munich, Germany; Omegametrix, Am Klopferspitz 19, D-82152 Martinsried, Germany. PMID 19520557 [archive] [PubMed - as supplied by publisher]</ref>:

* [[心率失常|心率失常]]
* [[动脉粥样硬化|动脉粥样硬化]]

=== 癌症===
多个研究表明，EPA或DHA摄入对[[乳腺癌|乳腺癌]]或者[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]的影响取决于同时摄入的omega-6脂肪酸和[[抗氧化剂|抗氧化剂]]<ref>Bagga D, Anders KH, Wang HJ, Glaspy JA. Long-chain n-3-to-n-6 polyunsaturated fatty acid ratios in breast adipose tissue from women with and without breast cancer. Nutr Cancer 42, (2002) 180-5.</ref><ref>Leitzmann MF, Stampfer MJ, Michaud DS, Augustsson KA, Colditz GC, Willett WC, Giovannucci EL., 2004. Dietray intake of n-3 and n-6 fatty acids and the risk of prostate cancer. Am J Clin Nutr; 80 : 204-216.</ref>。EPA亦对预防直肠结肠癌有效果<ref>Courtney, E.D., Matthews, S., Finlayson,C., Di Pierro, D., Belluzzi, A., Roda, E., Kang, J.Y., and Leicester, R.J., 2007. Eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) reduces crypt cell proliferation and increases apoptosis in normal colonic mucosa in subjects with a history of colorectal adenomas. Int. J Colorectal Dis.</ref>。

